# DevOps Guru
DevOps Guru is a python package that provides a simple interface for creating and deploying cloudformation templates to AWS.

## Installation
```python
pip install devops-guru
```

## Usage
```python
devops-guru --help
```

## Commands
```python
devops-guru create
```

```python
devops-guru deploy
```

```python
devops-guru delete
```

```python
devops-guru list
```

```python
devops-guru update
```

